query:
INSERT INTO exercise_repositories (
    id,
    course_id,
    url,
    deploy_key,
    public_key,
    STATUS,
    error_message
  )
SELECT uuid_generate_v5($1, id::text),
  $1,
  url,
  deploy_key,
  public_key,
  STATUS,
  error_message
FROM exercise_repositories
WHERE course_id = $2
  AND deleted_at IS NULL;
